Dia. 01 Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is a \cf1\b mistake\cf0\b0 . Probably White forgot that even if he captures the Black two stones he can't live.
\par
\par Black's placement at 2 is the vital point of the five space shape.
\par
\par If White plays at A, Black captures White with the throw-in.
\par
\par
\par }
