Dia. 02 Severe Placement
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is the 1-2 vital point, but it is wrong in this situation.
\par Black 2 is a \cf1\b severe placement\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par After White 3, Black destroys the eye with 4 and White can't live anymore.
\par
\par Be careful! If Black plays at 3 instead of 2, White lives with the dansu at A.
\par
\par }
