Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is the only vital point for saving this corner.
\par In some situation, the \cf1\b 2-2\cf0\b0  is the vital point.
\par It is the second most often used move in the corner.
\par
\par After Black 2, White can make two eyes with 3.
\par
\par }
